Dear D28 Community,

Please join us at the next Hybrid CEC 28 Annual and Business Meeting on Thursday, July 11, 2024, at 6:30pm. Please see the attached agenda for your reference.

CEC 28 July Hybrid Annual and Business Meeting

Date & Time: July 11, 2024, at 6:30PM

In-Person location: District 28 Office at 90-27 Sutphin Boulevard Jamaica, NY 11435

Or

Join Via ZOOM

Register here:

https://nycdoe.zoom.us/meeting/register/tJMkcuuurj4qHtUigi50g8Ho9HoNLx9bTXkD

Happy last day of the 2023-2024 school year!!

As a reminder, your child's report card can be found on their NYC Schools Account. It will not be printed and sent home.

If you do not have an account, please reach out to me and I will help you. It is very important to have this account set up already. You can view all information about your child on there.

www.schoolsaccount.nyc

Also, save this link. It's quick access to everything you may need.

https://linktr.ee/ps161q

Alisa Abrahim - Parent Coordinator

Babrahim@schools.nyc.gov

REMINDER!

PS 161 End of Year Award Ceremonies

Join us as Grades 1 - 5 celebrate all of their achievements!

Monday, June 10th -1st Grade

Tuesday, June 11th - 2nd Grade

Wednesday, June 12th - 5th Grade

Thursday, June 13th - 4th Grade

Friday, June 14th - 3rd Grade

All ceremonies begin at 8:15 in the school auditorium.

Please reach out to your child's teacher with any questions.

Join us as we go over some resources and activities that you can do over the summer.

Summer Resources - Virtual Parent Workshop

Tuesday, June 11 · 6:00 – 7:00pm

Zoom Meeting Link : https://zoom.us/j/98966883107?pwd=fzrno0JbIx6Ra6UZFcrUg0h6hJI1dB.1

Zoom ID : 989 6688 3107

Passcode : 062303

We will have a Spanish speaking translator!

See you soon!

Come join us on Friday, May 31st at 1pm. We always enjoy getting together and having great conversations.

Feel free to share any ideas and thoughts with our Principal, Ms. Hoder.

We will have refreshments!

REMINDER!

Kindergarten offers have already been sent out. Many of you have accepted but there are a few that never responded.

Remember, you will have to complete registration again. We are completing registration every day between 8am and 10am. You will need to bring your child's birth certificate/passport, two proofs of income and vaccine records.

If you have any questions, please reach out to me.
